These Truths
            

            <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">John Patrick Diggins</ENAMEX> is
living in a world of phantoms when he uses the myth of <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Lincoln</ENAMEX> as a hammer to
