of society. He also at times sympathized with the notion of <ENAMEX TYPE="NATIONALITY">American</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">blacks</ENAMEX>
returning to <ENAMEX TYPE="LOCATION">Africa</ENAMEX>. So how, exactly, does <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Diggins</ENAMEX> find <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Lincoln</ENAMEX> to be such a
